title: Obama says GOP candidates are like 'Grumpy Cat'
text: President Obama ridiculed congressional Republicans and the GOP presidential candidates Friday as "gloomy" doomsayers. " They are like Grumpy Cat, " Mr. Obama said, referring to a popular meme and making a frowning face. "Everything is terrible according to them. 'We're doomed!'"
